        </h2>
    </header>


        


<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="4521571">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/4521571/" class="title-link">文襄六王</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-4521571"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/speakingdoll/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u46893842-5.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/speakingdoll/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">speakingdoll</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-12-12"
      class="main-meta">2010-12-12 11:48:51</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_4521571_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  前些天在书市上买了北齐书。鲁迅说过，书要买小而薄，拿在手里最省力气。翻到文襄六王列传，没头没尾地看。我觉得对于非历史系的外行来说，史书里纪传部分都可以当小说的，反正又不考古勘校，又不求甚解，无论是孤史无证还是众说纷纭，看看热闹就好了。历史上真实的杀伐征戮，...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/4521571/#comments">(9回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">5有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_4521571_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_4521571_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="4512146">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/4512146/" class="title-link">读李百药《北齐书》</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-4512146"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/glenwang/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1144163-23.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/glenwang/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">汪杨</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-12-08"
